The '''Crimson Corridor''' was a high-crime district in the [[Third Quadrant]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant's]] [[Zi-Kree Sector]]. It was less than 10 kilometers from the [[Jedi Temple/Legends|Jedi Temple]].

==History==
One of the oldest areas of the city, the district contained the [[Follin Restaurant]], the [[Tusken Oasis]], the [[Green Glowstone Tavern]], [[Barsoom Boulevard]], and [[Lorn Pavan]]'s apartment near one end, and was the main territory for the [[Raptors (gang)|Raptors]].

A string of murders of police officers here in the waning years of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]] prompted law enforcement to develop the droid-piloted [[police cruiser backup unit]] for intensive patrols.

